                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8539" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1320</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2600 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">隆基绿能数智化转型提升绿色价值链之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Road to Longi&#39;s Digital and Intelligent Transformation to Improve The Green Value Chain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">林红珍，陈代思</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">隆基绿能科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">隆基绿能；数智化转型；绿色价值链；价值创造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> LONGi Green Energy;Digital and intelligent transformation; Green value chains; Value creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了在国际形势复杂多变、数智技术迅猛发展的背景下，隆基绿能坚守新能源企业“善用太阳光芒、创造绿能世界”的使命，积极利用数智化转型提升绿色价值链的实践过程。隆基绿能为绿色价值链各环节——研发、采购、制造、运输、营销、售后嵌入大数据、云平台、人工智能等领域的最新技术，达到节能降碳、降本增效的作用，使企业的绿色价值链创造出更大的价值。隆基绿能的数智化转型提升了核心竞争力、把握了“双碳”背景下的新机遇，也为其它企业利用数智化转型提升价值链提供了借鉴经验。本案例可以引导学员思考在“双碳”目标和绿色发展的背景下，能源企业如何紧跟时代前沿科技利用人工智能、大数据等技术条件，推动能源绿色低碳转型，建立安全高效的能源体系，进而引导学员树立数智化和绿色化高效耦合的双化思维。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case illustrates the practice process of LONGi Green Energy adhering to the mission of &quot;making good use of the sun&#39;s rays and creating a green energy world&quot; as a new energy enterprise against the backdrop of the complex and ever-changing international situation and the rapid development of digital intelligence technology, and actively using digital and intelligent transformation to improve the green value chain. LONGi Green Energy embeds the latest technologies in the fields of big data, cloud platform, and artificial intelligence into all links of the green value chain, including R&amp;D, procurement, manufacturing, transportation, marketing, and after-sales, to achieve energy saving, carbon reduction, cost reduction and efficiency improvement, and create greater value for the green value chain.LONGi Green Energy&#39;s Digital and Intelligent Transformation LONGi has improved its core competitiveness, grasped new opportunities in the context of &quot;dual carbon&quot;, and provided reference experience for other enterprises to use digital and intelligent transformation to improve the green value chain. This case can guide students to think about how energy companies can keep up with the cutting-edge technology of the times and use artificial intelligence, big data and other technical conditions to promote the green and low-carbon transformation of energy, establish a safe and efficient energy system in the context of the &quot;dual carbon&quot; goal and green development, and then guide the students to establish a dual-industrialization thinking of efficient coupling of digital intelligence and greening.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数智化转型；绿色价值链；价值创造；双化协同</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
                            </tr>
